        <h1 class="mt-5 font-bold leading-[1.05] text-5xl text-stone-900 tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
          Real food.<br>
          <span class="text-stone-500">Nothing else.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-md leading-relaxed text-lg text-stone-600">
          BareBowl makes freeze-dried and air-dried treats from a single, human-grade ingredient. No grains. No fillers. No mystery.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-8">
